description:
This is a 2003 PS2 game that emulates well with the PCSX2 version 1.1; this didn't work with the version 1.0, (at least not for me)

This is a shoot'em up game where you drive a specialized vehicle that drives on 

land and when needed, turns into a high speed boat, you also get out and 

kick ass on foot too, very neat game.

